  "body": "### Features\r\n\r\n- Add `home` and `end` keys and map them to scroll\\_{first,last}. (#126)\r\n- Add PageUp/PageDown support for Data Block view. (#125)\r\n- Add clipboard functionality with terminal multiplexer support. (#123)\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* feat: add clipboard functionality with terminal multiplexer support by @dferg in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/123\r\n* Add PageUp/PageDown support for Data Block view by @plaes in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/125\r\n* Home/end scrolling support by @plaes in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/126\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @dferg made their first contribution in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/123\r\n* @plaes made their first contribution in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/125\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/fioncat/otree/compare/v0.6.4...v0.6.5",
